{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reform public service pensions",
        "additional_details": "Many private sector workers struggle to build up an adequate pension, while public service pensions are more generous than most private pension schemes.\r\n \r\nWe want the Government to level the playing field between public and private pensions, and reduce the burden on the taxpayer.\r\n",
        "background": "With the cost of public service pensions falling on the taxpayer, we believe the current unfunded system for public service pensions is not fair or sustainable. We want the Government to introduce a new pension scheme that is fully funded by employer and employee pension contributions.",
